range_Icc_support:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr →₀ » -/
@[simp]
theorem range_Icc_support [DecidableEq ι] (f g : «expr →₀ » ι α) : (rangeIcc f g).support = f.support ∪ g.support := by
  convert rfl
#align range_Icc_support range_Icc_support

theorem mem_range_singleton_apply_iff : a ∈ f.range_singleton i ↔ a = f i :=
  mem_singleton
#align mem_range_singleton_apply_iff mem_range_singleton_apply_iff
mem_range_Icc_apply_iff:
theorem mem_range_Icc_apply_iff : a ∈ f.range_Icc g i ↔ f i ≤ a ∧ a ≤ g i :=
  mem_Icc
#align mem_range_Icc_apply_iff mem_range_Icc_apply_iff
